<h3>How to install Elementor Pro Nulled?</h3>
<p>To install the plugin <strong>you need to download the archive from us and unzip it</strong> using the unzipper program. Inside the archive you will find two plugins – <strong>free Elementor</strong> and premium (paid) <strong>Elementor PRO</strong>.<br />
Plugins must be downloaded through the WordPress menu <strong>Plugins - Add New</strong>. If you don't have the free Elementor installed, you need to install and activate both the free and the paid (PRO) parts of the plugin. <strong>If the free part is already installed, you don't need to install it again!</strong></p>
<p>Once you install Elementor PRO, you will have access to all premium features of the plugin, <strong> including premium templates from Elementor</strong> template library. Please note, in order to have premium templates you need to create a free account on the official site.</p>
<h3>How do I activate Elementor Pro?</h3>
<p>If you purchase and download the Elementor PRO plugin from our site, you do not need to activate your license. <strong>We provide an already activated (pre-activated) version for an unlimited number of domains (websites)</strong>, so you can install, use or transfer the pro version of the plugin without any restrictions.</p>
<h3>Is the PRO Templates and Kit Library available?</h3>
<p>Yes, after installing the pro-version you have access to <strong>Pro templates library (blocks)</strong>, as well as<strong> Kit Library.</strong> Each PRO kit from Kit Library includes a complete set of headers, footers, content of regular and archive pages, global design settings (color, typography, etc.). So <strong>you can create a complete site with the necessary content and design in just a couple of clicks!</strong></p>
<p>In order to import a kit into your Kit Library, go to <strong>Elementor - Tools - Import/Export Kit</strong>, then click <strong>Start Import</strong> and select the zip file from the <strong>Kit Library</strong> folder, which you will find inside the archive with the plugin.</p>
<p>After importing the selected kit you get a fully populated with pages and content site with customized design and functionality.</p>
